The verbatim prompts reproduced under skills/*/references/prompt.md,
skills/paper-orchestra/references/anti-leakage-prompt.md, and
skills/paper-writing-bench/ and skills/paper-autoraters/ are excerpted from:

  Song et al., "PaperOrchestra: A Multi-Agent Framework for Automated AI
  Research Paper Writing", arXiv:2604.05018, 2026.

Those excerpts are the intellectual contribution of the paper's authors and are
reproduced here for the sole purpose of faithful implementation. Please cite
the paper when using this software.
